name: Experiment Or Die #47
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Yesterdays design was about the end of Hicetnunc but that death was short lived as it only took a few hours for it to be reborn almost exactly the same. Can't really say that of the Cybermen though. Their hosts were reborn but as these horrific robotic zombies. Lets hope the new Hen turns out better than that. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
